  "name": "Purchase Orders - Matrix Ordering Spreadsheet",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"purchase-orders-matrix-ordering-spreadsheet\">Purchase Orders - Matrix Ordering Spreadsheet</h1>\n<p>The Purchase Order Matrix Ordering Spreadsheet is a tool developed outside of Retail Express, exclusively within Microsoft Excel. The spreadsheet is updated, then uploaded into Retail Express.</p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Please note: </strong>This file is only compatible with Windows computers, and cannot be used on Mac. The tool is provided \"as is\" and requires advanced<strong> </strong>knowledge of Microsoft Excel. Support and training on the Matrix Ordering spreadsheet is not available.</p>\n</div>\n<p>Using the tool you can:</p>\n<ul><li>Create new products with sizes and colours based on the Manufacturer SKU (also referred to as the Style Code/Model)</li><li>Create a standard PO Upload Template ready for uploading into Retail Express</li></ul><p> </p>\n<h2 data-id=\"using-the-matrix-ordering-spreadsheet\">Using the Matrix Ordering Spreadsheet</h2>\n<ol><li><br/><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.retailexpressmedia.com%2Fimplementation%2Fdownloads%2FMatrixProductsandOrdersV2020-1.xlsm\">Click here to begin download</a><br/><div><br/><strong>Important: </strong>Ensure you <strong>save the file to your computer </strong>and <strong>keep the original filename</strong>,<strong> </strong>otherwise the tool will not work</div><br/></li><li>Open the file in Microsoft Excel</li><li>Click <strong>Enable Editing<br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003111315/mceclip0.png\" alt=\"mceclip0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003111315/mceclip0.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003111315/mceclip0.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003111315/mceclip0.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003111315/mceclip0.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003111315/mceclip0.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003111315/mceclip0.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003111315/mceclip0.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></strong><br/></li><li>Click <strong>Enable Content </strong>(this will enable the advanced automated features of the tool)<br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003181976/mceclip2.png\" alt=\"mceclip2.png\" width=\"394\" height=\"23\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 23px; width: 394px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003181976/mceclip2.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003181976/mceclip2.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003181976/mceclip2.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003181976/mceclip2.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003181976/mceclip2.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003181976/mceclip2.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003181976/mceclip2.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Press the <strong>OK</strong> button on the welcome screen</li><li>Begin by entering the main information at the top:<br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003244175/mceclip0.png\" alt=\"mceclip0.png\" width=\"520\" height=\"155\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 155px; width: 520px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003244175/mceclip0.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003244175/mceclip0.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003244175/mceclip0.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003244175/mceclip0.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003244175/mceclip0.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003244175/mceclip0.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003244175/mceclip0.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Enter your <strong>Outlet Name </strong>in the red box</li><li>Enter your <strong>Supplier Code </strong>in the red box; this is the code as entered in Retail Express.<br/><div><br/><strong>Note: </strong>You will need to create separate files for multiple suppliers</div><br/></li><li>If using an eCommerce integration with <strong>Sales Channels </strong>and <strong>Source Groups</strong>, enter the names into each field on the right</li><li>Each product is broken up into its own \"Lines\" - a section separated into details on the left, and size/colour information on the right. When the PO Matrix template is run this will create individual lines in the resulting PO spreadsheet. </li><li>Enter your <strong>product information</strong> - Style Code, Description, SupplierBuyEx price, POS Price (only required when creating a new product), Brand, Season, Product type<br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003158156/mceclip2.png\" alt=\"mceclip2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003158156/mceclip2.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003158156/mceclip2.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003158156/mceclip2.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003158156/mceclip2.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003158156/mceclip2.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003158156/mceclip2.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003158156/mceclip2.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Edit the Size/Colour headings to match the sizes and colours required for ordering<br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086055/mceclip5.png\" alt=\"mceclip5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086055/mceclip5.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086055/mceclip5.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086055/mceclip5.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086055/mceclip5.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086055/mceclip5.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086055/mceclip5.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086055/mceclip5.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Enter the quantity for each combination; if a combination is not required leave the field blank<br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086015/mceclip4.png\" alt=\"mceclip4.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086015/mceclip4.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086015/mceclip4.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086015/mceclip4.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086015/mceclip4.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086015/mceclip4.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086015/mceclip4.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360003086015/mceclip4.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Repeat steps 9 to 11 for additional products</li><li>Click <strong>Create Order</strong><br/></li><li>To prepare the file for the next supplier, click <strong>Reset Order</strong><br/></li></ol><h2 data-id=\"frequently-asked-questions\"><br/><a name=\"Faqs\" id=\"Faqs\"></a>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<div><br/><div>\n<h4 data-id=\"can-i-use-this-file-for-products-to-be-published-on-shopify\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#shopify-po-matrix\">Can I use this file for products to be published on Shopify?</a></h4>\n</div><br/><div id=\"shopify-po-matrix\"><br/><div>\n<p>You can use this file to create your products and Purchase Orders, however you <strong>won't </strong>be able to mark the products to be published to Shopify as the data required for products is unique for Shopify stores, and cannot be automatically created through this tool.</p>\n<p>In order to create your products and orders for Shopify you should:</p>\n<ol><li>Use the Purchase Orders Matrix Spreadsheet following the instructions above</li><li>Upload the file into Retail Express (creating your products and orders)</li><li>Use the Mass Download feature to download a list of your Products in Retail Express</li><li>Follow the instructions in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Publish-Products-to-Shopify\">Shopify - Product Synchronisation</a> article section \"Publishing/Adding Products\" for multiple products<br/><div><br/><strong>Note: </strong>This will allow you to select products to be published online in bulk</div><br/></li></ol><p> </p>\n</div><br/></div><br/></div>",
